{"tid":1010050,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[初二宜投票]#文詠珊 李佳芯 朱晨麗 朱千雪 2018-19 LIHKG香港女神總會盃十六強投選專區","createTime":"2019-02-05T15:59:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T17:10:29.000Z","uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ca96ada749e3ef5079f50875e534cc093ee3b49a","tid":1010050,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T15:59:38.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:00am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n(超)文詠珊vs林泳淘(冠)<br />\n(超)李佳芯vs朱智賢(甲)<br />\n(冠)朱晨麗vs苟芸慧(超)<br />\n(超)朱千雪vs張曦雯(超)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27bcf0687e187cd6448b68ab98c42f212252e098","tid":1010050,"uid":92376,"like":121,"dislike":36,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T16:00:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-19 LIHKG香港女神總會盃十六強</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*括號內數字為聯賽排名(非聯賽者則以非聯表示)</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2019-2-6 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/tzLSmzo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtzLSmzo.png&h=01bb5b00&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/yHkxusX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyHkxusX.png&h=0fa264f8&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(超3)文詠珊vs林泳淘(冠3)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"4f023e1a8c4d2c57dd17be1a6a8e5f284f7e345d","tid":1010050,"uid":92376,"like":139,"dislike":18,"score":121,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2019-2-6 12:02am-10:02pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Edm3OXT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEdm3OXT.png&h=95cb63e4&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ljkod1c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fljkod1c.png&h=59f39773&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(超1)李佳芯vs朱智賢(甲4)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"cb83fa7e6d8f05963ded23625f8e22fe2fb883a7","tid":1010050,"uid":92376,"like":66,"dislike":88,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T16:04:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2019-2-6 12:04am-10:04pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/M2yUSnG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FM2yUSnG.png&h=2a0ff170&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/KM5wjn4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKM5wjn4.png&h=12e9e091&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(冠2)朱晨麗vs苟芸慧(超5)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"7fb4520a86602a550d8164622ce7431afc38aaf6","tid":1010050,"uid":92376,"like":110,"dislike":38,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T16:06:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2019-2-6 12:06am-10:06pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ZMiKj8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZMiKj8L.png&h=8ca84104&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/NK2BTLt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNK2BTLt.png&h=e8aa85b3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(超4)朱千雪vs張曦雯(超11)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"f4def0bd9101c5f7eb533dac00d089bc25ecc265","tid":1010050,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T16:06:48.000Z","msg":"(超)倪晨曦vs鄺潔楹(乙)<br />\n(超)陳法拉vs沈卓盈(超)<br />\n(超)陳瀅vs謝安琪(超)<br />\n(甲)湯洛雯vs馮盈盈(超)<br />\n<br />\n明天同樣時間另外4場賽事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346298f61011723c3291136664e19d51613b9dd5","tid":1010050,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T02:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25fea4bcd9badd5d46492b11f464912ead5f2a7a","tid":1010050,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:48:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":